Package com.stormpath.sdk.organization

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CreateOrganizationRequest
    Represents an attempt to create a new Organization record in Stormpath.
    CreateOrganizationRequestBuilder
    A Builder to construct CreateOrganizationRequests.
    Organization
    An Organization is a top-level container of Directories and Groups.
    OrganizationAccountStoreMapping
    An OrganizationAccountStoreMapping represents the assignment of an AccountStore (either a Group or Directory) to a Organization.
    OrganizationAccountStoreMappingCriteria
    An OrganizationAccountStoreMapping-specific Criteria class, enabling an OrganizationAccountStoreMapping-specific fluentquery DSL.
    OrganizationAccountStoreMappingList
    A CollectionResource containing OrganizationAccountStoreMapping instances.
    OrganizationAccountStoreMappingOptions<T>
    OrganizationAccountStoreMapping-specific options that may be specified when retrieving OrganizationAccountStoreMapping resources.
    OrganizationCriteria
    An Organization-specific Criteria class, enabling a Organization-specific fluent query DSL.
    OrganizationList
    A CollectionResource containing Organization instances.
    OrganizationOptions<T>
    Organization-specific options that may be specified when retrieving Organization resources.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OrganizationAccountStoreMappings
    Static utility/helper methods for working with OrganizationAccountStoreMapping resources.
    Organizations
    Static utility/helper methods for working with Organization resources.
